#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.plot.scatter.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.plot.scatter"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:1
#: of
msgid "Create a scatter plot with varying marker point size and color."
msgstr "创建一个具有不同标记点大小和颜色的散点图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:3
#: of
msgid ""
"The coordinates of each point are defined by two dataframe columns and "
"filled circles are used to represent each point. This kind of plot is "
"useful to see complex correlations between two variables. Points could be"
" for instance natural 2D coordinates like longitude and latitude in a map"
" or, in general, any pair of metrics that can be plotted against each "
"other."
msgstr ""
"每个点的坐标由两个 DataFrame 列定义，并使用填充圆圈表示每个点。这种图"
"有助于查看两个变量之间的复杂相关性。点可以是例如地图中的经度和纬度等自然"
"二维坐标，或者通常是可以相互绘制的任何一对度量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner
#: of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:10
#: of
msgid ""
"The column name or column position to be used as horizontal coordinates "
"for each point."
msgstr "用作每个点的水平坐标的列名或列位置。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:13
#: of
msgid ""
"The column name or column position to be used as vertical coordinates for"
" each point."
msgstr "用作每个点的垂直坐标的列名或列位置。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:16
#: of
msgid ""
"The size of each point. Possible values are:  - A string with the name of"
" the column to be used for marker's size.  - A single scalar so all "
"points have the same size.  - A sequence of scalars, which will be used "
"for each point's size   recursively. For instance, when passing [2,14] "
"all points size   will be either 2 or 14, alternatively."
msgstr ""
"每个点的大小。可能的值包括：- 一个字符串，表示用于标记大小的列名。- 一个"
"单一标量，使所有点具有相同的大小。- 一个标量序列，将递归地用于每个点的"
"大小。例如，当传入 [2,14] 时，所有点的大小将交替为 2 或 14。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:16
#: of
msgid "The size of each point. Possible values are:"
msgstr "每个点的大小。可能的值包括："

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:18
#: of
msgid "A string with the name of the column to be used for marker's size."
msgstr "一个字符串，表示用于标记大小的列名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:20
#: of
msgid "A single scalar so all points have the same size."
msgstr "一个单一标量，使所有点具有相同的大小。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:22
#: of
msgid ""
"A sequence of scalars, which will be used for each point's size "
"recursively. For instance, when passing [2,14] all points size will be "
"either 2 or 14, alternatively."
msgstr ""
"标量序列，将递归地用于每个点的大小。例如，当传递[2,14]时，所有点的大小将"
"交替为2或14。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:26
#: of
msgid ""
"The color of each point. Possible values are:  - A single color string "
"referred to by name, RGB or RGBA code,   for instance 'red' or '#a98d19'."
"  - A sequence of color strings referred to by name, RGB or RGBA   code, "
"which will be used for each point's color recursively. For   instance "
"['green','yellow'] all points will be filled in green or   yellow, "
"alternatively.  - A column name or position whose values will be used to "
"color the   marker points according to a colormap."
msgstr ""
"每个点的颜色。可能的值包括：- 一个通过名称、RGB 或 RGBA 代码指定的单一"
"颜色字符串，例如 'red' 或 '#a98d19'。- 一个通过名称、RGB 或 RGBA 代码指定"
"的颜色字符串序列，将递归地用于每个点的颜色。例如 ['green','yellow']，所有"
"点将交替填充为绿色或黄色。- 一个列名或位置，其值将根据色彩映射为标记点着"
"色。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:26
#: of
msgid "The color of each point. Possible values are:"
msgstr "每个点的颜色。可能的值包括："

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:28
#: of
msgid ""
"A single color string referred to by name, RGB or RGBA code, for instance"
" 'red' or '#a98d19'."
msgstr ""
"一个通过名称、RGB 或 RGBA 代码指定的单一颜色字符串，例如 'red' 或 '#"
"a98d19'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:31
#: of
msgid ""
"A sequence of color strings referred to by name, RGB or RGBA code, which "
"will be used for each point's color recursively. For instance "
"['green','yellow'] all points will be filled in green or yellow, "
"alternatively."
msgstr ""
"按名称、RGB或RGBA代码引用的颜色字符串序列，将递归地用于每个点的颜色。例如"
"['green','yellow']，所有点将交替填充为绿色或黄色。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:36
#: of
msgid ""
"A column name or position whose values will be used to color the marker "
"points according to a colormap."
msgstr "一个列名或位置，其值将根据色彩映射为标记点着色。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:39
#: of
msgid "Keyword arguments to pass on to :meth:`DataFrame.plot`."
msgstr "传递给 :meth:`DataFrame.plot` 的关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner
#: of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:41
#: of
msgid ":class:`matplotlib.axes.Axes` or numpy.ndarray of them"
msgstr ":class:`matplotlib.axes.Axes` 或它们的 numpy.ndarray"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:45
#: of
msgid ":py:obj:`matplotlib.pyplot.scatter`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:46
#: of
msgid "Scatter plot using multiple input data formats."
msgstr "使用多种输入数据格式的散点图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:49
#: of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:50
#: of
msgid ""
"Let's see how to draw a scatter plot using coordinates from the values in"
" a DataFrame's columns."
msgstr "让我们看看如何使用 DataFrame 列中的值作为坐标来绘制散点图。"

